<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1362220" n="1"/>
  <note hand="pers_DE-588-135542286">Ad <rs type="person">D. Raillardum</rs>.</note>
<opener><lb/><salute>Vir Clarissime et Doctissime, Amice plurimum honorande.</salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Vellem equidem et ego, ut occasio minus tristis Tibi affuisset,<del><gap/></del>
  <lb/><rs type="letter">literis Tuis</rs> <add>me</add> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>veniendi, et ut <del><gap/></del>mihi animo magis l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>to responsio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem ad Te dare liceret. Sed quia Dei voluntate factum est, ut
  <lb/>luctus <del><gap/></del><add>quem</add> ex morte <rs type="person">Parentis <add>mei</add></rs> concepi, Te participem esse<del><gap/></del>
  <lb/>mihi <del><gap/></del>significares, <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quum est, ut pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentibus debita, sed tristi,
  <lb/>gratiarum actione erga Te defungar. Rem <del><gap/></del>fecisti amico dign<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
  <lb/>mihique gratissimam, dum <del><gap/></del><add>me monuisti</add> tanto luctu<add>i</add> <del><gap/></del>lacrymis, ut
  <lb/>vere dicis, majori silentium <del><gap/></del>optime convenire, <add>dumque</add> mihi<del><gap/></del>
  <lb/>ad justissimum dolorem aliquando vincendum fortem animum
  <lb/><add>quo certe opus habeo</add> precatus es. Quod <del><gap/></del><add>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea</add> tam honorifice de defuncto <rs type="person">Patre meo</rs>
  <lb/>senseris, non minores ago gratias;<del><gap/></del> et
  <lb/>est quod solatium mihi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>beat, si alii viri boni Tui similes et Pa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tri<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> amantes mecum lugeant, licet jactura quam fecit <rs type="place">Patria</rs>
  <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>si modo fecit<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> minime sit comparanda cum ea quam fecimus ego
  <lb/>et <rs type="person">familia</rs> <del><gap/></del>mea. Parum enim prodesse potuit <abbr>Reip.</abbr> <rs type="person">Pater</rs>,
  <lb/><del><gap/></del><add>cujus</add> voluntas <add>in Patriam prona</add>, <del><gap/></del><add>qualem</add> certe habuit, ob eam ipsam quam di<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cis corruptionem, s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>pius successu caruit. At ego sane multum
  <lb/>perdidi, et quotidie experior quam <!-- ToDo: kontrollieren, ob vor rare noch etwas zusätzlich steht --><del><gap/></del>rare reddant
  <lb/>vulnus meum ea qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> dixisti negotia <add>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim</add> sub initium muneris<del><gap/></del>
  <lb/><del><gap/></del>fastidiosa, absentia <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> propinquis, familiaribus et amicis,
  <lb/>et vita, quam hic dego, fere solitaria. Vix enim est unus aut alter
  <lb/>cum quo familiariter vivere possim, et plerique <rs type="person">Professores</rs> nostri
  <lb/>mihi sunt barbari aut ego illis. In id tamen enitar, ut animum
  <lb/>erigam et dolorem vincam.</p>
<closer>Tu autem Vale et literis Tuis primas
  <lb/>secuturis exhilara amicum Tuum
  <lb/><signed><rs type="person">NB.</rs></signed>
  <dateline><date when="1717-02-24">24. <abbr>Febr.</abbr> 1717.</date></dateline>
</closer>
</div>
